{"tid":310774,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"除左水果，咩都唔想食","createTime":"2017-07-06T05:44:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-07T05:01:12.000Z","uid":374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0f454783643a320e5ff7ef52e6a22683dcf2fafc","tid":310774,"uid":374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T05:44:05.000Z","msg":"我都知咁樣好唔健康<br />\n但唔知點解自己以前一直都係食嘢好快嘅人<br />\n而家越食越慢<br />\n除咗食水果之外都冇乜胃口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n午餐淨係水果為主，食兩三個水果加個包，但個包都好辛苦先吞到落肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢D是咪厭食？<br />\n但我唔想減肥，已經偏瘦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88e5ce49e33add80a83f1c7579136ed2562b17c3","tid":310774,"uid":374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T05:46:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99215a6a9e5a12a9499209582e0f9190381c3844","tid":310774,"uid":374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T06:35:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b9c3829c3f171ae7a091df67122ad0c89f2dfcf7","tid":310774,"uid":75100,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T06:38:50.000Z","msg":"我都係無咩胃口.....<br />\n呢個情況，我覺得睇中醫會有用.....<br />\n<br />\n你鐘意食生果，可能代表你體內好乾，所以你食有水份既野就覺得舒服d，相反食包呢d又硬又粘既，就覺得好難吞落去，你調理返好個身體，就淨食白飯都覺得好味架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你都無可能一世食水果架嘛"},{"pid":"20a07f41242ff475bcbfd202fffd6e1575dbc181","tid":310774,"uid":108956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T06:39:21.000Z","msg":"食太多會糖尿病"},{"pid":"6805a1bfabbd09d7d280aa7eb14d36ab245b8514","tid":310774,"uid":374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:28:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係無咩胃口.....<br />\n呢個情況，我覺得睇中醫會有用.....<br />\n<br />\n你鐘意食生果，可能代表你體內好乾，所以你食有水份既野就覺得舒服d，相反食包呢d又硬又粘既，就覺得好難吞落去，你調理返好個身體，就淨食白飯都覺得好味架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你都無可能一世食水果架嘛</blockquote><br />\n你又啱，巴打睇過中醫？"},{"pid":"1d49bce5367a61d2d180b09cf3355cde5c91d6bd","tid":310774,"uid":374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:29:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食太多會糖尿病</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 除左水果其餘都盡量清淡的<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15ff2e7df6a4d83fea6303584ca5270d0c73dc00","tid":310774,"uid":37153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:33:36.000Z","msg":"係咪有病 <br />\n以前我一日都未必飲到杯<br />\n依加日日食十幾杯以上"},{"pid":"f8c9c656c73a8e550e994f336e3e392ba6242ba0","tid":310774,"uid":118776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:37:39.000Z","msg":"去睇醫生好d<br />\n我以前都有厭食 每日剩係食白粥 <br />\n食左好長一段時間<br />\n如果要食其他野 要飲好多水呑佢落去<br />\n一食完野或者飲完水就會肚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最輕果時係 165cm 35kg<br />\n而家正常去返43kg"},{"pid":"63928d0dce1fb76c50ccd45e9a6cf90952f48f4c","tid":310774,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:48:50.000Z","msg":"以前抑鬱症食唔到野，連最鍾意食嘅炒蛋都含喺口入面吞唔落，剩係食到流質嘅野或者水果，後尾睇咗醫生先逐漸食得返野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b533602affbffc73a44cd628fff1fa0927c5d261","tid":310774,"uid":75100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T16:11:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前抑鬱症食唔到野，連最鍾意食嘅炒蛋都含喺口入面吞唔落，剩係食到流質嘅野或者水果，後尾睇咗醫生先逐漸食得返野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n吉野妹而家見你餐餐大魚大肉wo <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cdb74620da820f415d5b2508be22e676415fdbb","tid":310774,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T01:16:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>以前抑鬱症食唔到野，連最鍾意食嘅炒蛋都含喺口入面吞唔落，剩係食到流質嘅野或者水果，後尾睇咗醫生先逐漸食得返野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n吉野妹而家見你餐餐大魚大肉wo <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n抑鬱症好多年前啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"343747f6870d9b2ee77edebef649a9a712767764","tid":310774,"uid":374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T02:43:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去睇醫生好d<br />\n我以前都有厭食 每日剩係食白粥 <br />\n食左好長一段時間<br />\n如果要食其他野 要飲好多水呑佢落去<br />\n一食完野或者飲完水就會肚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最輕果時係 165cm 35kg<br />\n而家正常去返43kg</blockquote><br />\n43kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇醫生食藥？"},{"pid":"8ddb2e9bf2cc9b081001e4cd9ba18e50271da473","tid":310774,"uid":18117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T03:26:29.000Z","msg":"水果食得多傷脾胃, 惹濕<br />\n你咁樣只會越黎越冇胃口"},{"pid":"b490ca2eae1b46f71dff681190982607cc60796e","tid":310774,"uid":118776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T04:53:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去睇醫生好d<br />\n我以前都有厭食 每日剩係食白粥 <br />\n食左好長一段時間<br />\n如果要食其他野 要飲好多水呑佢落去<br />\n一食完野或者飲完水就會肚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最輕果時係 165cm 35kg<br />\n而家正常去返43kg</blockquote><br />\n43kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇醫生食藥？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇左一排醫生 醫depression 同anxiety <br />\n後尾自己生活調節返 就冇再厭食<br />\n不過depression同anxiety就未好返"},{"pid":"33a653c64e450d6fe639451af43712d6ca47d112","tid":310774,"uid":92459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T05:01:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪有病 <br />\n以前我一日都未必飲到杯<br />\n依加日日食十幾杯以上</blockquote><br />\n你以前有病, 依加正常"}]}